assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: SAKURA KCS Corporation provides information technology services in Japan. It develops and sells application software and package software products to customers in various industries comprising finance, public, manufacturing / distribution / service, etc. The company also provides data center, cloud, business process outsourcing, hosting, and outsourcing services comprising data entry and printing, and contract calculation services, as well as IDC services, such as housing services. In addition, it designs and builds IT infrastructure, such as system infrastructure and network environment; and engages in computer maintenance work, as well as sells various computer equipment, and related peripherals and equipment. SAKURA KCS Corporation was incorporated in 1969 and is headquartered in Kobe, Japan.
